<p>I've seen a fair share of super robot shows introduce a proper gattai sequence at a surprisingly late point in the story, but Baxingar really takes it to the extreme. Episode 27 of 39, and only now do we get our first glimpse of the polished combination.<br>
<br>
Looks great, but damn...</p>
